follow(String, double[]) - Method in class it.unicam.cs.followme.util.EntityInterpreter
FOLLOW command allows the entity to move towards a certain condition signaled by other entities within a certain distance.If the distance of the condition which is calculated from the average of the sums of the entities positions is less or equal than the given distance, than the entity will follow it otherwise the direction will be calculated within the range [-dist][dist]
